      <title>特朗普要求无限期推迟其封口费判决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/trump-asks-for-indefinite-delay-for-his-hush-money-sentencing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普请求纽约一名法官无限期推迟对其刑事封口费案的宣判，以便美国法官有时间充分考虑将此案移交联邦法院的请求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/trump-asks-for-indefinite-delay-for-his-hush-money-sentencing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 20:46:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
